WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.206 --> 00:00:02.320
Wait, wait.

2
00:00:02.669 --> 00:00:08.074
Allow me to contribute the following lines regarding this meeting.

3
00:00:09.374 --> 00:00:10.475
In response.

4
00:00:15.690 --> 00:00:17.094
Our unerring fate

5
00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:19.847
is to be deceived in everything we try.

6
00:00:22.844 --> 00:00:26.681
Every morning I make great plans.

7
00:00:29.849 --> 00:00:31.209
and mess around all day.